Los_Angeles.Elysian Valley, Los Angeles: Elysian Valley, also known as Frogtown, is a neighborhood of more than 7,700 residents within Central Los Angeles, California, adjoining the Los Angeles River. It has a large percentage of children between the ages of 11 and 18 and a high number of Latinos and Asians. There is one elementary school in the neighborhood, Dorris Place Elementary School, but children have also historically attended Allesandro Elementary School.
